---
title: Double Creamy Bacon & Veggie Pasta Bake with Cheddar Cheese
description: Cheese has always been married to pasta, they are inseparable. Make their bond even stronger by baking a thick layer of Cheddar on
top of the pasta. Watch as it embraces the fusilli, bacon and veggies in a warm — and very tasty — hug. It’s a match made in heaven!
